Description:
You enter a small chapel near the forest border, it appears to have been recently looted. You hear a noise behind some benches and then a trembling voice says:

"Oink... are they gone? Oink... Yogger wants to eat me, he sent his werewolves for me.

Please... please... Oink... help me, defeat Yogger so I can leave this chapel. I am a very capable priest and I will help you in your future travels... Oink."
DescriptionAction: The scared pigman is dressed as a holy priest.
